@21   = ~I pray to Lathander, that you may be right. She... means much to me.~
@22   = ~Naturally.~
@23   = ~I have some special weapons here. Please take your pick, <PRO_LADYLORD> <CHARNAME>. None of them are more valuable than her safe return.~
