/* new for v12.2.0 */
@5042  = ~Through Berronar's divine powers, the silver arm of a guardian golem was fused to the stump of Breagar's arm. Breagar can now use this hand, as if it were his own. The metal is enhanced by a blessing of the dwarven goddess, allowing Breagar to block weapons and even magical attacks to some extent. Unfortunately, the fingers of this new hand are too thick for wearing rings.

Breagar success fully managed to incorporate meteorite ore into the hand, and improved its resistance to damage.

STATISTICS:

  Strength Bonus: +1
  Armor Class: -3 bonus
  Saving Throws: +3 bonus~

