While journeying through the Underdark, <CHARNAME> and Breagar found the lost gems and repaired the axe in Cromwell's smithy. This deed awoke the interest of the dwarven gods, and they blessed the weapon with additional powers. Since then the axe shines in new-found splendor and is now a formidable weapon against evil, especially against giants and their kind.

